-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                 |                      |1       |641         |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE              |                      |1       |641         |
|2 |  └─TOP-N SORT                     |                      |1       |641         |
|3 |    └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN             |                      |1       |641         |
|4 |      ├─HASH JOIN                  |                      |1       |636         |
|5 |      │ ├─MERGE JOIN               |                      |1       |261         |
|6 |      │ │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN        |income_band           |9       |4           |
|7 |      │ │ └─SORT                   |                      |1       |256         |
|8 |      │ │   └─MERGE JOIN           |                      |1       |256         |
|9 |      │ │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |household_demographics|200     |14          |
|10|      │ │     └─SORT               |                      |4       |229         |
|11|      │ │       └─HASH JOIN        |                      |4       |228         |
|12|      │ │         ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|customer_address      |4       |37          |
|13|      │ │         └─TABLE FULL SCAN|customer              |1000    |107         |
|14|      │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |store_returns         |3000    |124         |
|15|      └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET      |customer_demographics |1       |16          |
=====================================================================================
